org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.api.network

Interface INetworkElementProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NetworkElementProviderEmpty, NetworkElementProviderPartContainer, NetworkElementProviderSingleton

    public interface INetworkElementProvider
    Capability that can create instances of an INetworkElement. Blocks that provide this capability MUST properly call NetworkHelpers.onElementProviderBlockNeighborChange(World, BlockPos, Block, Direction, BlockPos).
